{
  "key_path": "AiServicesManagementDescription",
  "content": "Control the activation of AI features across {{productName}} and {{organizationName}} editors. When disabled, the {{aiSettings}} section will be hidden, {{aiAgents}} will be unavailable to all users (with history preserved), and the paid {{organizationName}} {{aiServices}} will no longer be accessible. However, all interaction history with the AI will be securely saved and fully restored upon re-enabling {{aiServices}}.",
  "content_en_sha1_hash": "804862e60d57ab10abceb8ef36877c2a3d804896",
  "created_at": "2026-03-26T08:26:46.818Z",
  "updated_at": "2026-05-15T14:00:06.769Z",
  "comment": {
    "text": "This is a descriptive text that appears below the \"AI Services Management\" setting. It explains the consequences of disabling AI features, including hiding the {{aiSettings}} section, making {{aiAgents}} unavailable, and restricting access to paid {{aiServices}} for {{organizationName}}. It also clarifies that interaction history will be preserved and restored upon re-enabling {{aiServices}}.",
    "is_auto": true,
